      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Reserved tier requires a 12-month commitment. Teams must forecast usage at sign-up. Over-commitment wastes the discount; under-commitment spills to Standard pricing for the excess. Build a commitment tracking reconciler that flags teams whose actual usage is >20% below their reservation."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Markup Schedule Design"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Observability (5\u20138%)"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Spans, traces, cost attribution, anomaly detection. The platform cannot be managed without it \u2014 charge for it explicitly."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Guardrails (3\u20135%)"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": PII redaction, content filtering, jailbreak detection. Compliance-critical; teams cannot opt out."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Fallback routing (2\u20133%)"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Circuit-breaker logic, provider health checks, secondary model invocations. Reduces team-level outage risk."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Shared infra (4\u20136%)"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": API gateway, secrets management, VPN egress, model registry. Fixed cost distributed proportionally to usage."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Total markup of 14\u201322% is typical for a mature internal platform. Below 10% suggests platform costs are being under-recovered. Above 30% creates incentives for teams to bypass the platform and call providers directly \u2014 undermining governance and observability."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Impact Analysis Before Publishing a New Version"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Publishing a new rate card changes costs for every team simultaneously. Before each version, estimate the spend delta per team using their trailing 3-month usage and notify teams whose annual cost changes by more than 5%."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "codeBlock",
        "attrs": {
          "language": "python"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "from dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Optional\n\n@dataclass\nclass RateCardChangeProposal:\n    proposed_version: int\n    reason: str                   # \"provider_price_change\" | \"quarterly_review\" | \"new_service\"\n    provider_price_changes: list[dict]\n    markup_changes: list[dict]\n    estimated_team_impact: dict[str, float]   # team -> delta in annual spend USD\n    requires_approval: bool\n\n    @property\n    def is_material(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"Material if any team's annual spend changes by > 5%.\"\"\"\"\n        return any(abs(v) > 0.05 for v in self.estimated_team_impact.values())\n\ndef estimate_team_impact(\n    old_card: RateCard,\n    new_card: RateCard,\n    monthly_usage: dict[str, dict[str, int]],   # team -> {service_name -> tokens}\n) -> dict[str, float]:\n    \"\"\"\n    Compute annual spend delta per team under the new rate card.\n    monthly_usage: trailing 3-month average, extrapolated to 12 months.\n    \"\"\"\"\n    delta: dict[str, float] = {}\n    for team, services in monthly_usage.items():\n        old_annual = 0.0\n        new_annual = 0.0\n        for service, tokens in services.items():\n            # assume 50/50 input/output split for simplicity\n            input_t = tokens // 2\n            output_t = tokens - input_t\n            try:\n                old_annual += compute_charge(old_card, service, input_t, output_t) * 12\n                new_annual += compute_charge(new_card, service, input_t, output_t) * 12\n            except KeyError:\n                pass\n        delta[team] = (new_annual - old_annual) / old_annual if old_annual else 0.0\n    return delta"
          }
        ]
      },
